있다#{19}":[74,121],"##A Grand Experiment Opening a New Chapter in Rural Healthcare in America — RHTP":[122,174],"##A Grand Experiment Opening a New Chapter in Rural Healthcare in America — RHTP#{1}":[124,174]},"outlinks":[{"title":"San Lee","target":"San Lee","line":5}],"metadata":{"title":"미국 농촌 의료의 새로운 장을 여는 거대한 실험","source":"https://www.mediontech.com/migug-nongcon-yiryoyi-saeroun-jangeul-yeoneun-geodaehan-silheom-rhtp/","author":["[[San Lee]]"],"published":"2026-04-11","created":"2026-04-11","description":"농촌 의료의 미래는 ‘기술 도입’이 아니라 ‘운영체계 재설계’에 달려 있다몇 달 동안 저는 네바다의 농촌 의료 전환 프로그램(Rural Health Transformation Program, RHTP)을 따라가며 많은 문서와 구조, 파트너십, 벤더, 운영모델을 들여다봤습니다. 처음에는 이것이 네바다의 기회처럼 보였습니다. 하나의 주정부 프로그램, 하나의 재정 기회, 하나의 지역 전략. 하지만 깊이","tags":["#clippings"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:Clippings/미국 농촌 의료의 새로운 장을 여는 거대한 실험.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1ojmhwm","at":1775917853499},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03296745,-0.02855732,0.0549187,-0.05659276,0.04456848,-0.0350471,0.01110837,0.02718916,-0.02739845,-0.02290714,-0.00195159,-0.07946625,0.06403837,0.04690977,0.02048601,-0.03172623,0.02874574,0.03793665,-0.03074846,-0.00813107,0.09403129,-0.02560913,0.04867531,-0.06130824,0.06966975,0.02311568,0.00998504,-0.05996271,-0.07448308,-0.15690102,0.02203997,0.05644695,0.06580227,0.01534452,-0.02134418,0.01376601,-0.02836106,0.07732534,0.00485875,0.03199519,0.0164652,-0.00326222,-0.02005102,-0.03782777,-0.03134518,-0.03202257,-0.00198755,-0.06804919,-0.00303609,0.00044356,-0.04118529,-0.04812023,0.04547926,0.02154367,0.04366508,-0.00592099,-0.00679768,0.07966138,0.05767075,-0.0030836,0.03566404,0.06204423,-0.22302949,0.092372,-0.02598488,0.01756199,0.01381768,0.01011896,0.02093551,-0.03155775,-0.02714699,0.05667492,0.01367532,0.02348389,-0.04242165,0.00719095,0.00086183,-0.01210601,-0.06793275,-0.04492697,-0.0077941,0.0465401,0.00033384,-0.03497081,-0.03515652,-0.00229078,-0.02032671,-0.1136871